Package: snirh.lab
Type: Package
Title: Convert Laboratory Water-Quality Data to SNIRH Import Format
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-10-21
Authors@R: c(
    person("Luís", "Pereira", , "d57177@alunos.uevora.pt", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0628-4847"))
  )
Description: Convert laboratory water-quality data into the official file
    format used by Portugal's 'Sistema Nacional de Informação de Recursos Hídricos'
    (SNIRH), including parameter/unit mapping, basic validation rules, and export
    helpers. See APA's SNIRH overview (Agência Portuguesa do Ambiente) <https://apambiente.pt/agua/sistema-nacional-de-informacao-de-recursos-hidricos-snirh>
    and the government service description <https://www2.gov.pt/servicos/consultar-o-sistema-nacional-de-informacao-de-recursos-hidricos>.
